Usage: createMarker [-help] [-desc <description>] [-layer <layerName>]
                    [-rulemap] [-subtype <subtypeName>] [-tool <toolName>]
                    [-type <typeName>] {-bbox {x1 y1 x2 y2} | -poly {x1 y1 x2 y2 ...} | {{x1 y1} {x2 y2} ...}}

-help                          # Prints out the command usage
-bbox {x1 y1 x2 y2}            # Specifies the area of the bounding box of the
                               # marker. (string, optional)
-desc <description>            # Describes the marker. (string, optional)
-layer <layerName>             # Specifies the layer. (string, optional)
-poly {x1 y1 x2 y2 ...} | {{x1 y1} {x2 y2} ...}
                               # Specifies the area of the bounding polygon of
                               # the marker.. (string, optional)
-rulemap                       # Specifies if create the marker through
                               # ruleMap. (bool, optional)
-subtype <subtypeName>         # Specifies the marker subtype.
                               # (string, optional)
-tool <toolName>               # Specifies the source software application.
                               # (string, optional)
-type <typeName>               # Specifies the marker type. (string, optional)